@node requirements
@title "Requirements"

 All you need is the one and only MUI (Magic User Interface) by Stefan Stuntz!

 ... and of course an Amiga ... or was it Amooga (which appears by  courtesy  of
 Amiga International Inc. / Gateway 2000).

@endnode

@node install
@title "How to install??"

 To install just grab the GR directory, which contains all  images/buttons,  and
 copy or drag it into the MUI:Images directory.

 Then simply set up the images/buttons as a whole or  in  parts  using  the  MUI
 preference program.

 It should not be that hard to install ...
 
@endnode

