@node distribution
@title "Distribution"

 The 'GR-MUI-Images' set is Copyright © 1997 by Georg Rottlaender.


 'GR-MUI-Images'  may  be freely distributed as long as the following conditions
 are fulfilled:

 - all files have to be kept together and

 - no file may be modified (especially the images/buttons itself).

 Including  this  set  of  MUI  images/buttons  in  a  commercial  or  shareware
 distribution, is prohibited without my written  permission.

@endnode

